@@ySeal Testimony@@W                                       Sentinel level 50

Syntax: seal testimony

Preserve your current testimony marks against disruption. For 3 rounds:
  * Stun effects reduce testimony by only 1 mark instead of half.
  * Target-switch penalty reduced to losing 2 marks instead of full reset.
  * Flee/recall and target death still reset marks fully.

@@yDetails:@@W
  * Mana cost: 10
  * Requires at least 1 testimony mark.
  * Cannot stack.

Use this in long boss fights where a stun at 7+ marks would devastate your
verdict setup. The Tribunal sealed records against tampering — this is that
practice applied to your accumulated observations.

See also: @@msentinel testimony verdict@@W
